DESCRIPTION:
STRATEGY: Functional E2E API Lifecycle.
        Tests the full 'Happy Path' of a resource from birth to death.
NAME: test_note_full_lifecycle

DESCRIPTION:
STRATEGY: Negative Testing / Boundary Value Analysis.
        The API documentation requires titles to be at least 4 characters.
NAME: test_create_note_with_too_short_title_fails

DESCRIPTION:
STRATEGY: Boundary/Enum Testing.
        Verifies that the API correctly rejects categories not in the allowed list.
NAME: test_create_note_with_invalid_category_fails[Vacation]

DESCRIPTION:
Test Case: Verify that a registered user can log in via the UI.
        Target: https://practice.expandtesting.com/notes/login
NAME: test_successful_notes_login[chromium]

DESCRIPTION:
STRATEGY: Boundary/Enum Testing.
        Verifies that the API correctly rejects categories not in the allowed list.
NAME: test_create_note_with_invalid_category_fails[12345]

DESCRIPTION:
STRATEGY: Robustness / Error Handling.
        Verify API behavior when mandatory 'title' is missing.
NAME: test_create_note_with_missing_required_fields

DESCRIPTION:
STRATEGY: Hybrid - Mass Data Injection.
    Injects 3 notes via API and verifies UI renders the correct count.
NAME: test_mass_api_notes_appear_in_ui[chromium]

DESCRIPTION:
STRATEGY: Boundary/Enum Testing.
        Verifies that the API correctly rejects categories not in the allowed list.
NAME: test_create_note_with_invalid_category_fails[School]

DESCRIPTION: Test Case: Verify that invalid credentials trigger the correct UI error message.
NAME: test_invalid_notes_login[chromium]

DESCRIPTION:
STRATEGY: Authentication check.
        Verifies that requests without a token are rejected with 401.
NAME: test_unauthorized_access_is_rejected

DESCRIPTION:
STRATEGY: IDOR (Insecure Direct Object Reference).
        Ensures User B cannot delete User A's data even if they have the ID.
NAME: test_cross_user_deletion_is_forbidden
